snippet.title: Half Empty Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Half Empty is a 2D minimalist platformer that explores how feelings of self doubt affect the creative process. The game was created entirely by one man - Gary Alfonso. All writing, programming, art, and music were created by Gary Alfonso!
